title: 2017 Week 8 preview: Updated ‘lock’ standings & can the Chargers upset the Pats?
itunes:title: 2017 Week 8 preview: Updated ‘lock’ standings & can the Chargers upset the Pats?
description:
A room filled with some heroes- Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler & Gregg Rosenthal discuss Dan’s vending machine conspiracy theory (8:00); A preview of all of the Week 8 action, including which Raiders team will show up against the Bills on Sunday (16:30); Marc has a Sessler about the Chargers-Patriots game (24:00); Will the Jets get off the schneid and break their losing skid? (32:00); Can Deshaun Watson continue to give Texans fans hope in Houston’s matchup with Seattle? (44:00); A review of the “lock” standings for the season (55:00); And much more heading into Week 8.
